  <brief_title>Efficacy of Esomeprazole in Patients With Frequent Heartburn</brief_title>
  <acronym>NEXT2</acronym>
  <official_title>A Phase III Multi-Center, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Parallel Group Trial of 14 Day Treatment With Esomeprazole 20 mg Once Daily in Subjects With Frequent Heartburn</official_title>
  <sponsors>
